extends layout

block content
  h1 Diff of HTMLs
  p An unofficial diffs between <a href="https://html.spec.whatwg.org/">WHATWG HTML Standard</a> and <a href="https://w3c.github.io/html/">W3C HTML 5.1 Editor's Draft</a>.

  h2 Table of contents of the HTML specifications
  p as of ...
  ol
    each chapter in index
      li
        | #{chapter.heading}
        if chapter.sections
          ol
            each section in chapter.sections
              li
                - var href = '/diff/' + section.htmlPath
                a(href=href)
                  - var heading = section.heading === '__pre__' ? '(preface)' : section.heading
                  | #{heading}
                  span.icons
                    if section.whatwg
                      img.whatwg(alt='WHATWG', src='/images/whatwg.svg')
                    if section.w3c
                      img.w3c(alt='W3C', src='/images/w3c.svg')
